Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎 什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天早上
